{panel:bgColor=#eae6ff}
*Description*

As part of the Dashboard Improvements initiative, we want to update the navigation for logged in active users and that includes adding a new {{Add-ons}} navbar item to the desktop navbar.

The add-ons navbar link should open the add-ons drawer and should contain the current week param. So if the user is on the dashboard for week W05, clicking on the new navbar link should open {{/my-deliveries/2026-W05/withMenuAddOns}}. If the same user goes to check their next delivery, let‚Äôs say for W07, then the navbar link should open {{/my-deliveries/2026-W07/withMenuAddOns}}.

